(167, '1543724831', 'sjtu', 'LoveBridge', '○ [代挂][pic]88年复旦博士后GG诚征女友 ', '希望能在交大鹊桥遇到心仪的另一半。以下是个人情况介绍及内心期待：\n有意愿认识的姑娘可添加微信联系：273211657。\n\n关于我：\n生日：1988年劳动节生人；\n星座：金牛座；\n籍贯：河南郑州；\n身高：178 cm；\n学历：博士；\n毕业院校：西南大学(211本科，当年考清华落榜被调剂过去)，中科院物理所(硕博)；&#1\n60;&#160;&#160; \n目前工作：复旦大学博士后；\n工作经历：曾担任三本SCI学术期刊英文编辑；\n居所：目前住在复旦大学提供的博士后公寓，两室一厅，如此也为后续置业提供了一定缓\n冲。\n\n关于性格爱好：\n性格和顺，孝敬父母长辈，能做到及人之老；\n为人豪爽，读书这些年结交了不少知交好友，四散在大江南北海内海外(都是可以去轻心骚\n扰蹭吃蹭喝那种)；\n平时喜欢读书，文史哲以及专业方面的外文书均有涉猎，在同辈中应该算是博览群书了；\n喜欢文字游戏，闲常无聊会杜撰各种中英文打油诗词（下附）；\n喜欢看芭蕾、话剧、昆曲等各类演出；\n喜欢爬山徒步随拍；\n其他兴趣随涨随落，不过也都有过。\n\n个人生活理想：\n寻常风景亦需寻常人以不寻常眼观；\n等闲岁月也要等闲人以不等闲身试。\n\n关于家庭：\n非独生子女，普通家庭，父母开明，家庭美满和睦，父慈子孝。父母为我和哥哥的成长和\n教育提供了力所能及的支持，我们也非常感恩父母为我们所付出的。\n\n希望对方\n身高：160+ cm\n年龄：＜30岁(1989及以后出生)\n性格爱好：善良孝顺，有同理心，积极上进，能相互沟通和理解，喜欢阅读，有个人爱好\n和想法，对于未来的生活有所期待同时也有一些耐心等待(因个人置业尚需一些时日，暂时\n无法一蹴而就)，此外若是有一些才艺则属锦上添花。\n\n<IMG SRC="/file/LoveBridge/1543724758179930.jpg" onload="if(this.width > screen.width - 200){this.width = screen.width - 200}"><br/>\n\n<IMG SRC="/file/LoveBridge/1543724768180750.jpg" onload="if(this.width > screen.width - 200){this.width = screen.width - 200}"><br/>\n\n附一些打油诗词和随拍照片，以显示个人的一些才艺：\n\n1.采桑子\n远近丘山都望将，几亩秋塘。钓得云光，高林疏淡影投荒。\n归来天气始觉晚，草树都黄。染了晨霜，细草迷离掩晴芳。\n\n2.The Legend\nDescending from heavenly splendor,\nI am roaming around and look for\nMy true love. Are you dwelling in the earthly world?\nTo find you the extravagant palace is left behind, \nEthereal snow is my mind, the floating lotus my beating heart, \nThere are starry blocks on the (milk)way, \nSo many setbacks I never met, \nThe deep blue in my eyes, moonlight is shedding out,\nThough I can count drips in the hourglass, threads of the silk I never could, \nDrops condense into dew, threads woven into my travelling coat,\nTrekked in woods, waded through water, \nThe gray on my temples, are mingled with cloud,\nWherever you go, I will follow, or you see the grief hidden in my heart,\nI am afraid to see your ambition fading away, and hear you leaving no word,\nMy vow is like iceberg that never melt, \nAnd I will stay with you as an old friend,\nLet your hesitation be frozen, and let us hand in hand, \nDo not leave me in the cold, even though gossips still make you shake,\nIn the dream last night, I saw horse trotting through land, and you wearing th\ne red,\nYoked in marriage under gorgeous roof, sweet music enchants us till I wake,\nRoses blossom like mixed blood, climax is lingering in the heart,\nDressed up with headwear and veil, you take me to see the blueprint,\nSuccess will come in the end, you can trailblaze the wonderland with no wait,\nLet us cherish every moment together,\nUntil the stars turn into dust.\n\n手机随拍：\n\n<IMG SRC="/file/LoveBridge/1543724801180290.jpg" onload="if(this.width > screen.width - 200){this.width = screen.width - 200}"><br/>\n\n<IMG SRC="/file/LoveBridge/1543724809180180.jpg" onload="if(this.width > screen.width - 200){this.width = screen.width - 200}"><br/>\n\n<IMG SRC="/file/LoveBridge/1543724817179610.jpg" onload="if(this.width > screen.width - 200){this.width = screen.width - 200}"><br/>\n\n<IMG SRC="/file/LoveBridge/1543724823180670.jpg" onload="if(this.width > screen.width - 200){this.width = screen.width - 200}"><br/>\n\n--\n    爱是恒久忍耐，又有恩慈；爱是不嫉妒，爱是不自夸，不张狂，不作害羞的事，不求自己的益处，不轻易发怒，不计算人的恶，不喜欢不义，只喜欢真理；凡事包容，凡事相信，凡事盼望，凡事忍耐；爱是永不止息。', '', 0, '0', '273211657', '', 'bbstcon,board,LoveBridge,reid,1543724831.html', 'volcanozhang', 6028, 'bbsqry?userid=volcanozhang', '2018-12-02 04:27:00', '2018-12-03 10:41:28', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
